    <p class="small">Contemporary service similar to Modernist on shared components + slightly higher on mixed-chain items. Discovery legacy parts often command 15-30% premium over Modernist due to lower stock depth + aftermarket cross-reference sourcing on some components. Generation identification at diagnostic sets accurate expectations.</p>
