  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>LA service areas — Dacor oven concentrations</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>Beverly Hills + Bel Air luxury</h4><p><a href="/beverly-hills/">Beverly Hills</a> · Bel Air · Holmby Hills · Trousdale · Beverly Hills Flats</p></div>
